  <title>Access to safe WASH in the Teso and Karamoja</title>
  <description type="1">Support WaterAid Uganda in efforts to provide water, sanitation, and hygiene education services to the poorest people living in the Teso and Karamoja regions and make a tremendous impact in these communities. Beyond simply improving health, the benefits of safe water and sanitation are fundamental rights that help communities escape the cycle of poverty and achieve improvements in education and economic status, and most importantly &#x2013; a better quality of life. Support from the Aqwalife Foundation could provide crucial assistance in transforming the lives of 2,000 Ugandans over the next three years.</description>
